channel.title: 562 Element X Help
channel.description:
Hello.
I have coded and owning 317's for a long time now.
I eventually found out I wanted to try 562's and I wanted to host one, and I picked Element-X Source/Client
But, I have putted the source up on the VPS, and putted the VPS ip into the client and compiled successfully, and each time I try I get a error_game_js5connect.
tried several sources and none work. Heard this was a common problem with 562's.
Anyone know how to solve this? All help is greatly appreciated.
thanks
